{"tid":2376672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大肚婆被捕｜火爆警前科纍纍 曾庭上多次改口供 遭官質疑不可信不可靠","createTime":"2021-01-23T03:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T06:55:07.000Z","uid":239336,"like":163,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"7c489278ce14f3f9ef0fbfa6797d97bb006d8b97","tid":2376672,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:46:08.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣一名孕婦聲稱於周三被警員辱罵「死肥婆」，其後更被指阻差辦公，據悉有份處理今次案件的警長為黎錦耀（PC51195），翻查資料他早在2014年已有多次「火爆」前科，先是被投訴向截查市民爆粗，又向記者做「開槍」手勢，更涉嫌推撞投訴警方旅遊巴沒停車熄匙的酒店職員。至前年10月，網民在多區發動「神獸罷鷲」行動，兩名學生被指在深水埗參與集結遭拘捕，同被控在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，黎在庭上多次改口供，被裁判官質疑他的證供，指他的供詞不可信亦不可靠。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當時在現場的警長黎錦耀（PC51195），是警隊近年冒起最快的「火爆警」，本周三（20日）他不減火爆性格，當眾指對方的肚是假，甚至粗暴拉扯對方，惡行令人髮指。從女事主胞弟拍攝的片段顯示，黎錦耀當時與同袍截查女事主身份證時，態度非常惡劣，呼呼喝喝，其中黎錦耀最是火爆，動手又動口，驟眼看去以為警察拘捕賊人，原來是查孕婦身份證。<br />\n<br />\n這名PC51195，近六年非常出位，火爆惡行接二連三，2014年，有市民投訴稱，7月14日晚在旺角山東街被當時為高級警員的黎錦耀截查。事後該市民點算準備存入銀行的鈔票時，黎竟向他爆粗稱：「我隻錶貴X過你全身喇！」市民感憤怒，致電999投訴。黎再爆粗說：「我呢次俾你害X死！」<br />\n<br />\n8月19日，黎在黃竹坑警校佔中演練時，曾三度向記者做出「開槍」手勢。同年10月4日，旺角一間酒店職員投訴警方徵用的旅遊巴停車沒有熄匙，遭十多名警員圍罵。其中一名職員更被「砌生豬肉」襲警，並以涉嫌公眾地方行為不檢被捕。黎疑當時有份推撞該名職員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gnFzTOdNW53VXtQNVlf_QWKJ0OY=/1040x584/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B64QN2ZLFBCU5DVQTPSV6XT3QE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgnFzTOdNW53VXtQNVlf_QWKJ0OY%3D%2F1040x584%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB64QN2ZLFBCU5DVQTPSV6XT3QE.png&h=1d6979f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210123/IVNPR6BTDFF43ILMR7SYOFY4D4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210123%2FIVNPR6BTDFF43ILMR7SYOFY4D4%2F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5E2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=64d99fff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210123%2FIVNPR6BTDFF43ILMR7SYOFY4D4%2F&h=06e10170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210123/IVNPR6BTDFF43ILMR7SYOFY4D4/</a>"},{"pid":"78391d7577d9ab9586864823a7ff22d4e7d7c683","tid":2376672,"uid":87780,"like":173,"dislike":1,"score":172,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"香港警察啱哂呢啲人渣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9093b3fcb6558f66353e259e835c884e578f200e","tid":2376672,"uid":24788,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"升職啦 <br />\n人才來嫁"},{"pid":"4bfce0ce273cc8a4c086cd17cadb39c55548f0b3","tid":2376672,"uid":59472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17554337728e62058d53309c9f88653921aa3ed","tid":2376672,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8990d3e3b79c890af0ccf43bf5cfe6e6a924c19","tid":2376672,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d674c9e205b0e753bfe1027af8a772209fc75b83","tid":2376672,"uid":116967,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:54:43.000Z","msg":"警隊代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c13dcdcaa3939a7a460cc4ba7f6ae218b45fe3","tid":2376672,"uid":27411,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"傷心狗骨都有得加做3條狗骨，仲唔係人才嚟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9c4474021485232f4a4ae7a697c20b7260b58e","tid":2376672,"uid":19